<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Menu</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/site.css" asp-append-version="true" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css" />
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container mt-5">
        <h1 class="text-center mb-4">Menu de Operações</h1>

        <div class="alert alert-info text-center">
            Escolha uma das opções abaixo para gerenciar as notas fiscais:
        </div>

        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
            <div class="row text-center" style="max-width: 800px;">
                <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 mb-4">
                    <a href="../NotaFiscal/CreateNotaFiscal" class="menu-item text-decoration-none">
                        <div class="icon-container mb-2">
                            <i class="fas fa-keyboard fa-3x text-primary"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h5 class="text-dark">Entrada Manual</h5>
                        <p class="text-muted">Insira notas fiscais manualmente</p>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 mb-4">
                    <a href="../NotaFiscal/CreateImportarExcel" class="menu-item text-decoration-none">
                        <div class="icon-container mb-2">
                            <i class="fas fa-file-excel fa-3x text-success"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h5 class="text-dark">Importar Excel</h5>
                        <p class="text-muted">Importe várias notas de um arquivo Excel</p>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="d-flex justify-content-end mt-4">
            <a href="/Home/Menu" class="btn btn-secondary">
                <i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i> Voltar
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>

</html>
